SINYUKELE ku-3 300 isibalo sabantu abahaqwe yi-Covid-19 (Coronavirus) kuleli kanti leli gciwane selidlule nabanye abantu abane osekubeke isibalo sabashonile ku-58. Lokhu kuvezwe nguNgqongqoshe wezeMpilo kuleli uDkt Zweli Mkhize ngoMsombuluko ebusuku. Izindaba ezizothokozelwa abaningi nokho ngukuthi isibalo sabantu asebelaphekile kuleli gciwane sinyuke ngo-165, okusho ukuthi sebewu-1 055 asebesindile. UMkhize uthe sekuhlolwe abantu abawu-121 510 kuleli kanti izibhedlela zikahulumeni nezizimele sezibambisene ukuqinisekisa ukuthi abantu bahlolwa ngokushesha. As at today, the number of confirmed #COVID19 cases are 3300, the death toll is now 58 and the number of recoveries have increased to 1055 pic.twitter.com/8qn7V0NKdQ  #listentotheexpertPublic & private laboratories, as well as academic units, have joined forces to ramp up testing for #COVIDãƒ¼19. Prof. Koleka Mlisana from the NHLS tells us more. pic.twitter.com/vWewkOkj5E